    tmp = (((v2 + 0.95 + v1 + 0.84) / (v2 + 0.03 / v1 + 0.86)) + (wp.cos(tmp + 1.00) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.48)))
    v2 = ((tmp - 0.95) * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.12) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.77)))
    v2 = 0.24
